OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy start with
OL,6,Fa few spots of rain possible. Then
OL,7,Fcloud gradually breaking up through
OL,8,Fthe day to give plenty of long sunny
OL,9,Fspells by the afternoon. Feeling warm
OL,10,Fin the sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry start with late sunny
OL,13,Fspells but soon turning cloudy with
OL,14,Frain pushing into the north of
OL,15,FAberdeenshire. Mostly cloudy and dry
OL,16,Fovernight with rain around northern
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
