OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy but mostly
OL,6,Fdry day, with occasional bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Thicker cloud in the
OL,8,Fnorth with some light rain possible.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FMostly dry on Thursday with variable
OL,12,Fcloud and sunny spells. Then becoming
OL,13,Fmostly cloudy on Friday and Saturday
OL,14,Fwith some outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,15,Feastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
